thread.title_full: Renovator Store reviewed by Michelle P

author: Michelle P
title: Michelle P
text: Great pop up screen on the website to ask any questions about the produce. Had fast delivery and no fuss. You can have piece of mind when buying the product that it can be returned and also had a warrenty included. The kitchen sink I bought has exceeded my expectations, I love it! Would highly recommend, great prices and excellent service.
